oji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全明你感受"},{"pid":"f169feba7484e265ff7d6cc52809a280ae9d29ba","tid":190841,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T23:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫我有野唔明唔識要問佢 <br />\n但問佢又會燥底 <br />\n到底想我點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全明白<br />\n以前有個上司又係咁<br />\n問佢又惡死又黑面<br />\n唔問又話要出聲問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf7adb521f8ad9a74d4549576486b4a144dcd69","tid":190841,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T23:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫我有野唔明唔識要問佢 <br />\n但問佢又會燥底 <br />\n到底想我點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同我上司完全一樣<br />\n問完又話你廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫你唔明就問係必需話你知，但唔代表你可以亂問。最少要証明你研究過，用個腦諗過過濾過先問。<br />\n例如:你要搵sample,佢要用10分鐘搵，但你要用30分鐘搵。你問佢佢就會覺得你自己曬多小小時間都做到既野仲問。<br />\n同埋問既時機好重要，佢趕緊野or心情唔好，你仲煩佢就等死la。"},{"pid":"887d04651e47e855e6bddd01ca7b0572afec9e00","tid":190841,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T00:00:08.000Z","msg":"自己醒水啦，咁樣點樣做落去姐？<br />\n你炒佢好過俾佢炒你啦<br />\n趁依家只係翻左5日，早d搵過一份，呢份垃圾就唔使寫落CV<br />\n如果唔係到時俾你捱幾個月先走，見新工會問你呢份工既問題，甚至打去問你依家條粉腸上司，到時你就趴街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d959d165ef766899ed92e563f3fd756617397b","tid":190841,"uid":43621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T01:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫我有野唔明唔識要問佢 <br />\n但問佢又會燥底 <br />\n到底想我點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌一樣"},{"pid":"1fe61149a864c7c35036d9